research/history/logs/agent_round_0149.stdout.log:691:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"revisit","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，E(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量静态 expert 子库选择 + expert 内 local top-k + 查表加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r148 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `two_stage_residual_expert` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“expert-internal low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert、低成本 recipe 下是否能优于现有 0.20x-0.22x 低成本锚点，并形成新的结构性前沿段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["若该点在约 0.20x 成本下明显优于当前 0.20x-0.22x anchor，则下一轮只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `K`，继续判断瓶颈在 shared basis 宽度还是 lookup 预算。","若该点仍明显劣于同成本 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 锚点，则可更明确地下调 `factorized_expert_topk` 以及相关 expert-internal low-rank 无 shared/residual 线的优先级。","若该点改善有限但比 r133 明显更好，则说明旧负信号主要受旧 recipe 影响；后续可保留该 family 作为低成本结构参考，但不应让其主导预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["r148 的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 在当前 matched recipe 下得到 FVU=0.1140，说明 trunk-free staged residual 仍未补出新的 <0.5x Pareto 段。","本地 allowlist 自检已通过：`factorized_expert_topk` 接受 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 这些当前 recipe 所需 override。","本地 smoke 已过：`factorized_expert_topk` 在 K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224 下可 instantiate 并 forward。","本地成本自检：该 recipe 下 `factorized_expert_topk` selection_ratio≈0.09、deployment_ratio≈0.11、combined_ratio≈0.20，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前 `expert_topk` 同 recipe 的约 0.23x。","旧的 r133 负信号来自不同 recipe（K=128、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320）；本轮是在当前 112/224/2-expert recipe 下做 fresh validation，不应直接把旧结果当结论。"],"reference_round":148,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r148 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。最近两轮 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert` 都没有形成新非支配点，继续在这些 family 上做局部旋钮微调信息增量很低；切到 `factorized_expert_topk` 能在当前 matched recipe 下补一条尚未被近期复验的 expert-internal low-rank 结构证据，而且总成本仅约 0.20x，正落在当前最需要补强的低成本带。主要风险是该 family 在旧 recipe 上已有负信号，但本轮正是为了验证这些负信号是否只是旧配置下的假阴性。","summary":"建议以 r148 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`。这是一次面向 0.20x 低成本带的结构复验，目标不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk`，而是直接回答“expert 内 low-rank local head”在当前 2-expert recipe 下是否能形成比现有低成本锚点更有价值的新段。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0133.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。在线侧可导出为“共享低秩投影 + 单 expert 路由 + expert 内 local top-k + 静态子库查表加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r132 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `two_stage_residual_expert` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答当前高优先级问题“expert 内部 low-rank head / local top-k”是否比 trunk-free staged residual 更值得继续；如果该 family 在约 0.21x total_cost 下明显优于现有 `expert_topk` / `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的低成本负信号，则说明当前低成本带更有价值的不是继续打磨旧 shared+routed 结构，而是把低秩限制放进 expert 内部 head。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.21x 下显著优于现有同级低成本 anchor，则下一轮保持 `factorized_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试 expert-internal low-rank 是否还能进一步左移。","如果该点只与 `expert_topk` 持平或更差，则可更清楚地判定“expert-specific low-rank head”在当前 target 上也不成立，后续应转向别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 上做局部扫参。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=factorized_expert_topk`、`factorized_hidden_dim=256`、`active_experts=1` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.09x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.21x，明显低于 r132 的 0.47x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮相对 r132 是纯架构切换，目标是补上当前 prompt 明确优先的“shared/low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”结构信息，而不是继续在已连续无改进的 family 上细扫。"],"reference_round":132,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r132 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert` 已连续给出非支配失败，继续在这两条线上调内部旋钮的信息增量不高；切到 `factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和 prompt 对 expert-internal low-rank 的明确指向。主要风险是该 family 历史上有弱信号，但那是旧轮次弱先验；本轮在当前 target 上用 matched recipe 重验，结论会更干净。","summary":"Round 133 应优先切到新的结构假设，而不是继续打磨最近两条已连续失利的 family。建议以 r132 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`，在约 0.21x 的更低总成本下直接检验“expert 内部 low-rank head + local top-k”是否能形成新的低成本结构前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0131.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert。在线侧可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r130 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r130 在约 0.29x total_cost 下的失败是否主要来自“always-on shared low-rank branch + single routed expert”这一异构组合本身；如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r130 的 FVU=0.2266，则说明当前低成本瓶颈更偏向 shared+routed 结构耦合，而不是单-expert lowrank+expert 这条线整体失效。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下显著优于 r130，则下一轮保持 `lowrank_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=32/48`，定位这条 `lowrank + expert` 线的低成本 knee。","如果该点仍接近或劣于 r130，则可更干净地判定当前 <0.3x 带里单-expert `lowrank + expert` 也不成立，后续优先转向 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在这两条线做局部打磨。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk`、`active_experts=1`、`trunk_rank=40` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, TRUNK_RANK=40, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","直接构造行为已自检，不再退化成 `topk`：`SparseCoder(..., architecture='lowrank_expert_topk')` 返回 `LowRankExpertTopKSparseCoder`，且 encode 输出与 `topk` 不同。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.11x、deployment≈0.16x、total≈0.28x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":130,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r130 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是回到 `lowrank_expert_*` 做局部扫参，而是基于 r129-r130 已给出的 shared-lowrank+routed 负信号，切到另一条高优先级未充分验证结构 `lowrank + expert` 做一次 matched-cost 架构对照；信息增量高于继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。主要风险是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在当前 target 也可能继续给出负结果；但那会把“<0.3x 带里单-expert lowrank+expert 是否值得继续”这个问题回答得更清楚。","summary":"Round 131 不继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做第三个非支配失败后的局部 probe，而是做一次 matched-cost 结构切换。建议以 r130 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，在近同样的 <0.3x 总成本下直接比较“shared low-rank + routed expert”与“low-rank trunk + single expert”谁更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0148.json:35:      "r147 \u7684 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` \u5728\u7ea6 0.55x \u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u4ec5\u5f97\u5230 FVU=0.1038\uff0c\u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u8bf4\u660e shared-lowrank hetero residual \u8fd9\u6761\u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u538b\u7f29 recipe \u4e0b\u6ca1\u6709\u80dc\u8fc7 r146 \u6216\u5f53\u524d `<0.5x` \u6700\u4f73\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0147.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式：x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 为 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 为 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 为全局 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 选择性 residual 补偿 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r146 只把 ARCHITECTURE 从 lowrank_expert_residual 切到 shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual，保持 K=112、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224、NUM_EXPERTS=64、STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 与其余训练配方不变，做一次 matched-cost 结构对照，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed expert + residual”在约 0.55x total_cost 下是否比当前 trunk-based lowrank_expert_residual 更值得继续。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["若该点在约 0.55x 成本下接近或优于 r146 的 FVU，则下一轮只改 K 或 STAGE1_RATIO，把这条 hetero-MoE+residual 线向 0.5x 左侧继续压缩。","若该点明显劣于 r146 且未优于 0.42x-0.55x 现有锚点，则可基本判定 shared-lowrank hetero residual 在线上价值不足，后续应停掉这条 family 的局部扫参。","若结果介于 r146 与 <0.5x frontier 之间但仍形成新的中成本非支配段，可把它作为 0.5x-0.7x 结构锚点，再只改一个压缩旋钮验证是否能形成稳定 Pareto 段。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已过：shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual 在 1024 维、K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224、STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 下可 instantiate 并 forward。","本地成本自检：shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual 在该配方下 selection_accesses=1843200、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=2301952，对 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.55，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","matched 对照基线 r146 的 lowrank_expert_residual 在同 K=112 recipe 下本地估算 combined_ratio≈0.54，因此本轮是有效的近同成本 architecture probe，而不是旧 family 的 K/LR 邻域微调。"],"reference_round":146,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r146 只改 ARCHITECTURE。当前高优先级问题是异构 MoE 的 shared+basis 版本在加入 residual 后是否还能成立；无 residual 的 shared-lowrank 线在 r141/r144 已给出较弱信号，但 shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual 早先在更高 K/更宽 expert 配方上出现过一次 keep，因此值得在当前更压缩、且与 r146 近同成本的 recipe 上做干净复验。风险是该 family 仍可能被 r146 直接压制；但即使失败，也能更明确地终止一条当前 agenda 中仍悬而未决的 hetero-MoE residual 方向。","summary":"建议基于 r146 做一次 matched-cost architecture swap：仅设置 ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual。它是 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，且在当前 K=112/EF=1 recipe 下本地估算总成本约 0.55x，正好回答当前最需要的结构问题：shared low-rank basis + routed expert + residual，是否比 trunk-based lowrank_expert_residual 更能形成新的中成本 Pareto 段。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0133.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d h(x)=ReLU(Bx) \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4\u6295\u5f71\uff0ce(h(x)) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u7684\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001 expert\uff0c{b_{e,i}} \u662f\u5404 expert \u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201c\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u79e9\u6295\u5f71 + \u5355 expert \u8def\u7531 + expert \u5185 local top-k + \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r132 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `two_stage_residual_expert` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=128`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u95ee\u9898\u201cexpert \u5185\u90e8 low-rank head / local top-k\u201d\u662f\u5426\u6bd4 trunk-free staged residual \u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u8be5 family \u5728\u7ea6 0.21x total_cost \u4e0b\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e\u73b0\u6709 `expert_topk` / `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` \u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u66f4\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6253\u78e8\u65e7 shared+routed \u7ed3\u6784\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u628a\u4f4e\u79e9\u9650\u5236\u653e\u8fdb expert \u5185\u90e8 head\u3002",
