research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1720:research/history/logs/agent_action_0134.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"192"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 256 降到 192，在保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变时，shared low-rank basis 仍能覆盖主要全局结构，而更窄的 shared scorer 不会显著伤害 routed expert 质量，从而把总成本从约 0.37x 压到约 0.35x，并直接回答当前最优先的 hetero MoE 线是否能通过进一步低秩化进入新的低成本结构前沿。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 在约 0.35x 下仍接近 r129 的 FVU=0.1219，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试这条 hetero MoE 线能否贴近 0.32x 带。","如果该点明显退化，则说明 shared branch 的低秩压缩空间已接近饱和，后续不应继续在该 family 上细扫 hidden width，而应转向新的结构假设或别的未充分验证 family。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `factorized_hidden_dim=192` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 允许 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` param-only override。","本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.22x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.35x，低于 r129 的 0.37x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":129,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r129 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 做旧 family 局部扫参，而是沿当前最有结构信息价值的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做一次定向低秩压缩，直接回应 prompt 对“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”方向的优先级。主要风险是该 family 在 r129 已接近但未进入 frontier，192 可能仍被现有 0.32x-0.37x 点支配；但这是当前最清晰的一次单变量结构压缩对照。","summary":"Round 134 建议回到当前最值得补信息的 hetero MoE 线，而不是继续在最近连续失败的 family 上切新架构。以 r129 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，用一次 matched-cost 压缩直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 是否能通过更窄 shared scorer 形成新的低成本结构锚点。","touched_files":[]}
