research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1779:research/history/logs/round0129_standard_1774835337.config.json:14:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1783:research/history/logs/agent_action_0128.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":108,"family_name":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，shared 子库与各 routed expert 子库都是真正静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared low-rank projection + shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”流水线；兼容性判断为直接兼容。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是不兼容，只能作历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：当前额外提示已明确要求停止把主要预算继续投入现有 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的局部扫参，而优先验证新的异构 MoE 结构信息；因此应先对刚完成集成的新 family 做一次最干净的 matched-cost 首轮验证。相对 r108 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`EF=1`、`adam`、`8e-4` 不变，直接回答“shared+routed experts + shared low-rank basis + expert-local top-k”是否能在相近或更低 total_cost 下优于现有 shared+routed 线。按当前成本模型，这个结构应主要压低 encoder selection 成本，而 deployment 成本与 r108 同量级，因此有机会在 <0.5x 带形成新的结构性前沿。","summary":"先不给新 family做局部扫参，直接做首轮 matched architecture swap。以 r108 为 reference，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 切到刚集成并已 smoke 通过的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，验证这条异构 MoE + shared low-rank basis 新结构是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r108 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不再继续沿 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做局部邻域延长，符合当前运行时优先级；也不新增 env key，因此无需改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。选择 r108 而不是更近的 r121-r123，是因为 r108 提供了当前新 family 最干净的 matched shared+routed recipe，且 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, K=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 已被证明是可行的强基线。主要风险是 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 shared basis 可能损失过多表达能力；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 已在 `sparsify/config.py` 和 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 实际落盘，并完成 instantiate/forward/backward 本地 smoke。","新 family 复用已有 tunables `NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，没有新增 env key。","本轮是对新增 family 的首个 matched validation，不应在首轮同时改 `K`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，否则无法清晰归因。","如果首轮结果异常，应先区分是训练稳定性问题还是结构负信号，而不要重新归因为注册链问题。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果新 family 在相近或更低 total_cost 下明显优于 r108，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=96`，测试这条新结构能否继续向更低 deployment 成本左移。","如果新 family有正信号但仍弱于预期，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，区分瓶颈是在 shared basis 宽度还是在 expert capacity。","如果新 family明显不如 matched `shared_routed_expert_topk`，则可较清晰判定当前 target 上这类异构 MoE 的 low-rank scorer 还不足以抵消表示损失，后续应切回别的未充分验证结构槽位，而不是继续细扫该 family。"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1785:research/history/logs/agent_action_0129.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 仍是不兼容 family，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r128 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r127-r128 的负信号是否主要来自“routed experts 也被一并 factorize”这一结构限制；如果是，则新 family 应在 fresh cost 约 selection=0.24x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.37x 的低成本带显著优于 0.2248，并决定这条 shared-lowrank + full-routed-head 结构是否值得继续扩展。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.37x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿，则下一轮保持新 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `K=112`，定位这条新线的 low-cost knee。","如果结果只小幅优于 r128 但仍明显差于现有 `<0.5x` frontier，则可初步判定问题不只在 routed factorization，本方向优先级应下调，后续转回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构。","如果训练前或 sanity 阶段出现新问题，先按新 family registration/forward 问题处理，不要把失败误判为结构质量结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","fresh cost 自检：selection_accesses=1015808、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=1540096，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.37，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":128,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：计划运行时相对 r128 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到旧 family 的局部扫参，而是落一个最小新原型，直接隔离“shared+routed 失败是否来自把 routed heads 也 factorize”这个高信息量结构问题。按 `sae-architecture-integration` 检查，whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 exact architecture smoke 都已完成；主要风险是 routed full heads 会把行为拉回接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而缺乏新的 Pareto 价值，但这本身也是清晰结论。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1786:research/history/logs/agent_action_0135.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"128"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r134 仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 192 进一步降到 128，在保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变时，shared low-rank basis 仍能承担主要全局结构，从而把总成本从约 0.35x 继续压到约 0.32x；如果 FVU 仍接近 r134 的 0.1248，则说明当前最有希望的低成本结构段就是这条 hetero MoE 线的进一步低秩压缩。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128` 在约 0.32x 下仍接近 r134，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=96` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=256`，继续测试这条 hetero MoE 线能否再向左推进。","如果该点明显退化，则说明 shared branch 的 low-rank 压缩已经接近极限，后续不应继续在该 family 上细扫 hidden width，而应切回新的结构假设。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `factorized_hidden_dim=128` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 允许 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` param-only override。","本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.20x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.32x，低于 r134 的 0.35x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":134,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r134 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。r134 已证明这条 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 线在 0.35x 仍保持接近 r129 的质量，继续把 shared scorer 从 192 压到 128 是当前信息增量最高、且仍符合“进一步稀疏化 + 进一步低秩化”指引的动作。主要风险是该点会被现有 0.30x-0.35x anchor 支配；但这正是本轮要确认的压缩边界。","summary":"Round 135 继续沿当前最有希望的 hetero MoE 线做一次更激进但仍清晰的单变量低秩压缩。以 r134 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 能否在约 0.32x 总成本下维持接近当前最强低成本结构点的质量。","touched_files":[]}
