research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:1902:research/history/logs/agent_round_0134.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"192"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧仍可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r129 仅把 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 256 降到 192，在保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变时，shared low-rank basis 仍能覆盖主要全局结构，而更窄的 shared scorer 不会显著伤害 routed expert 质量，从而把总成本从约 0.37x 压到约 0.35x，并直接回答当前最优先的 hetero MoE 线是否能通过进一步低秩化进入新的低成本结构前沿。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 在约 0.35x 下仍接近 r129 的 FVU=0.1219，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试这条 hetero MoE 线能否贴近 0.32x 带。","如果该点明显退化，则说明 shared branch 的低秩压缩空间已接近饱和，后续不应继续在该 family 上细扫 hidden width，而应转向新的结构假设或别的未充分验证 family。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `factorized_hidden_dim=192` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 允许 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` param-only override。","本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.22x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.35x，低于 r129 的 0.37x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":129,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r129 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 做旧 family 局部扫参，而是沿当前最有结构信息价值的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做一次定向低秩压缩，直接回应 prompt 对“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”方向的优先级。主要风险是该 family 在 r129 已接近但未进入 frontier，192 可能仍被现有 0.32x-0.37x 点支配；但这是当前最清晰的一次单变量结构压缩对照。","summary":"Round 134 建议回到当前最值得补信息的 hetero MoE 线，而不是继续在最近连续失败的 family 上切新架构。以 r129 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，用一次 matched-cost 压缩直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 是否能通过更窄 shared scorer 形成新的低成本结构锚点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:1903:research/history/logs/agent_round_0134.stdout.log:310:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d h(x)=ReLU(Bx) \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4\u6295\u5f71\uff0ce(h(x)) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u62e9\u7684\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001 expert\uff0c{b_{e,i}} \u662f\u5404 expert \u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201c\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u79e9\u6295\u5f71 + \u5355 expert \u8def\u7531 + expert \u5185 local top-k + \u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r132 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `two_stage_residual_expert` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=128`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u95ee\u9898\u201cexpert \u5185\u90e8 low-rank head / local top-k\u201d\u662f\u5426\u6bd4 trunk-free staged residual \u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u8be5 family \u5728\u7ea6 0.21x total_cost \u4e0b\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e\u73b0\u6709 `expert_topk` / `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` \u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u66f4\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6253\u78e8\u65e7 shared+routed \u7ed3\u6784\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u628a\u4f4e\u79e9\u9650\u5236\u653e\u8fdb expert \u5185\u90e8 head\u3002",
