CTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 做旧 family 局部扫参，而是沿当前最有结构信息价值的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 做一次定向低秩压缩，直接回应 prompt 对“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”方向的优先级。主要风险是该 family 在 r129 已接近但未进入 frontier，192 可能仍被现有 0.32x-0.37x 点支配；但这是当前最清晰的一次单变量结构压缩对照。","summary":"Round 134 建议回到当前最值得补信息的 hetero MoE 线，而不是继续在最近连续失败的 family 上切新架构。以 r129 为 reference，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，用一次 matched-cost 压缩直接测试 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 是否能通过更窄 shared scorer 形成新的低成本结构锚点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:1919:research/history/logs/agent_action_0131.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert。在线侧可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r130 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r130 在约 0.29x total_cost 下的失败是否主要来自“always-on shared low-rank branch + single routed expert”这一异构组合本身；如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r130 的 FVU=0.2266，则说明当前低成本瓶颈更偏向 shared+routed 结构耦合，而不是单-expert lowrank+expert 这条线整体失效。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下显著优于 r130，则下一轮保持 `lowrank_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=32/48`，定位这条 `lowrank + expert` 线的低成本 knee。","如果该点仍接近或劣于 r130，则可更干净地判定当前 <0.3x 带里单-expert `lowrank + expert` 也不成立，后续优先转向 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在这两条线做局部打磨。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk`、`active_experts=1`、`trunk_rank=40` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, TRUNK_RANK=40, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","直接构造行为已自检，不再退化成 `topk`：`SparseCoder(..., architecture='lowrank_expert_topk')` 返回 `LowRankExpertTopKSparseCoder`，且 encode 输出与 `topk` 不同。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.11x、deployment≈0.16x、total≈0.28x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":130,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r130 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是回到 `lowrank_expert_*` 做局部扫参，而是基于 r129-r130 已给出的 shared-lowrank+routed 负信号，切到另一条高优先级未充分验证结构 `lowrank + expert` 做一次 matched-cost 架构对照；信息增量高于继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。主要风险是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在当前 target 也可能继续给出负结果；但那会把“<0.3x 带里单-expert lowrank+expert 是否值得继续”这个问题回答得更清楚。","summary":"Round 131 不继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做第三个非支配失败后的局部 probe，而是做一次 matched-cost 结构切换。建议以 r130 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，在近同样的 <0.3x 总成本下直接比较“shared low-rank + routed expert”与“low-rank trunk + single expert”谁更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:1920:research/history/logs/agent_action_0133.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} α_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低维投影，e(h(x)) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert，{b_{e,i}} 是各 expert 的静态子库原子。在线侧可导出为“共享低秩投影 + 单 expert 路由 + expert 内 local top-k + 静态子库查表加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `factorized_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r132 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `two_stage_residual_expert` 切到 `factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答当前高优先级问题“expert 内部 low-rank head / local top-k”是否比 trunk-free staged residual 更值得继续；如果该 family 在约 0.21x total_cost 下明显优于现有 `expert_topk` / `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的低成本负信号，则说明当前低成本带更有价值的不是继续打磨旧 shared+routed 结构，而是把低秩限制放进 expert 内部 head。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.21x 下显著优于现有同级低成本 anchor，则下一轮保持 `factorized_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=128`，继续测试 expert-internal low-rank 是否还能进一步左移。","如果该点只与 `expert_topk` 持平或更差，则可更清楚地判定“expert-specific low-rank head”在当前 target 上也不成立，后续应转向别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_*` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 上做局部扫参。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=factorized_expert_topk`、`factorized_hidden_dim=256`、`active_experts=1` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.09x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.21x，明显低于 r132 的 0.47x，也低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮相对 r132 是纯架构切换，目标是补上当前 prompt 明确优先的“shared/low-rank basis + expert-specific head / local top-k”结构信息，而不是继续在已连续无改进的 family 上细扫。"],"reference_round":132,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r132 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 与 `two_stage_residual_expert` 已连续给出非支配失败，继续在这两条线上调内部旋钮的信息增量不高；切到 `factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前“结构扩展优先”和 prompt 对 expert-internal low-rank 的明确指向。主要风险是该 family 历史上有弱信号，但那是旧轮次弱先验；本轮在当前 target 上用 matched recipe 重验，结论会更干净。","summary":"Round 133 应优先切到新的结构假设，而不是继续打磨最近两条已连续失利的 family。建议以 r132 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`，在约 0.21x 的更低总成本下直接检验“expert 内部 low-rank head + local top-k”是否能形成新的低成本结构前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:1921:research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{l∈S_res(r1(x))} γ_l(x) c_l，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，r1(x)=x-Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i-Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}；U={u_i} 是静态 shared low-rank library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库，C={c_l} 是静态 residual library。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + 少量 routed experts 选择 + 静态库查表加权和 + 选择性 residual 补偿”，不依赖动态生成字典，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：当前最有信息量但尚无最小原型的槽位，不是再扫现有 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 的 hidden/K 邻域，而是给这条 hetero MoE 线补上一段全局 residual cleanup。相对 r134 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual cleanup”能否在约 0.60x total_cost 的中低成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该新 family 在约 0.60x 下明显优于 r134 且接近当前中成本最优点，则下一轮优先修好该 architecture 的 override allowlist，然后只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，区分瓶颈是在 stage1 shared+routed 容量还是 residual cleanup 配额。","如果该点有正信号但成本偏重，则下一轮在接好 allowlist 后只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 之一，测试 hetero MoE + residual 能否继续左移。","如果该点明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 或只小幅优于 r134，则可较清晰判定 residual 增益不足以抵消 shared+routed 的额外复杂度，后续应把预算转回别的兼容结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地编译通过：`python -m py_compile sparsify/config.py sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual, K=128, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，按 r134 配方（`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`）本地估算 selection≈0.47x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.60x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","本轮实际运行时相对 r134 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`；没有新增 env key，也没有改执行层语义。"],"reference_round":134,"self_review":"满足运行时单变量原则：计划运行时相对 r134 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 的旧 family 局部扫参，而是补齐当前高优先级但尚未实现的“hetero MoE + residual cleanup”最小原型。代码改动严格限制在 `sparsify/`，并已按 `sae-architecture-integration` 完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、concrete class 和 exact architecture smoke。主要风险是 residual encoder 的 1024x1024 选择成本本身就接近 0.25x，可能让该 family 的总成本落在 0.60x 左右却仍拿不到足够 FVU 改善；但这正是当前最需要的新结构证据。","summary":"已在 `sparsify/` 落盘最小新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`：把当前最有希望的 hetero MoE 原型 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 接上一段全局 sparse residual cleanup。建议本轮以 r134 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，先做一次干净的 matched architecture swap，直接判断“shared low-rank basis + routed experts + residual”是否值得继续。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
