research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:2258:research/history/logs/agent_round_0131.stdout.log:942:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert。在线侧可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r130 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r130 在约 0.29x total_cost 下的失败是否主要来自“always-on shared low-rank branch + single routed expert”这一异构组合本身；如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r130 的 FVU=0.2266，则说明当前低成本瓶颈更偏向 shared+routed 结构耦合，而不是单-expert lowrank+expert 这条线整体失效。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下显著优于 r130，则下一轮保持 `lowrank_expert_topk` 不变，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=32/48`，定位这条 `lowrank + expert` 线的低成本 knee。","如果该点仍接近或劣于 r130，则可更干净地判定当前 <0.3x 带里单-expert `lowrank + expert` 也不成立，后续优先转向 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构，而不是继续在这两条线做局部打磨。","真实训练启动后先检查 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` 与 checkpoint `config.json` 中 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk`、`active_experts=1`、`trunk_rank=40` 已落盘，再解释结果。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, TRUNK_RANK=40, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","直接构造行为已自检，不再退化成 `topk`：`SparseCoder(..., architecture='lowrank_expert_topk')` 返回 `LowRankExpertTopKSparseCoder`，且 encode 输出与 `topk` 不同。","当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 下，该 matched recipe 估算 selection≈0.11x、deployment≈0.16x、total≈0.28x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":130,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r130 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这不是回到 `lowrank_expert_*` 做局部扫参，而是基于 r129-r130 已给出的 shared-lowrank+routed 负信号，切到另一条高优先级未充分验证结构 `lowrank + expert` 做一次 matched-cost 架构对照；信息增量高于继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`。主要风险是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在当前 target 也可能继续给出负结果；但那会把“<0.3x 带里单-expert lowrank+expert 是否值得继续”这个问题回答得更清楚。","summary":"Round 131 不继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做第三个非支配失败后的局部 probe，而是做一次 matched-cost 结构切换。建议以 r130 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，在近同样的 <0.3x 总成本下直接比较“shared low-rank + routed expert”与“low-rank trunk + single expert”谁更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
