research/history/logs/agent_round_0139.stdout.log:3490:{"change_type":"edit_perf_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{j∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 是 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 是全局 residual 静态库，x_stage1 为 shared+routed stage 的重构。在线导出链路仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + 单 expert local top-k + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r138 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，利用 residual cleanup 吃掉少掉的第二个 routed expert 覆盖，从而把 total_cost 从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x，同时尽量保住 r138 的 FVU=0.0946，回答这条 hetero MoE + residual 线能否在 0.5x 左右形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 仍接近 r138 的 FVU，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 或 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 继续向 <0.5x 压缩。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显掉点，则说明这条线当前仍依赖双 expert 覆盖，下一轮优先回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 做 matched-cost 容量压缩，而不是继续削 router path。","若训练前 override 校验再次失败，应先检查 family-specific allowlist 是否被 runtime 热加载到最新代码，而不要把失败误判成架构结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的 AutoResearch override allowlist，真实改动仅在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","本地校验通过：`validate_env_overrides(..., fallback_architecture='shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual')` 现在接受 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`STAGE1_RATIO`，同时仍拒绝未消费的 `TRUNK_RANK`。","成本自检：在 r138 配方下把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 设为 1 后，selection_accesses=1646592、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=2170880，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.52，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":138,"self_review":"先修真实 blocker，再发实验：r138 已证明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 有结构价值，但此前它没有接入 family-specific override allowlist，后续任何合法的单变量 param-only 探针都会在训练前被判为 disallowed。当前已实际补上该 wiring，并做了本地 allowlist 自检。计划运行时相对 r138 只改 1 个 env 参数 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，满足单变量原则；风险是第二个 routed expert 仍对当前 target 很关键，导致 FVU 回退，但这会直接回答 residual stage 是否足以支撑更轻的 expert 激活路径。","summary":"已实际修复 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 的参数接线 blocker，使该新 family 后续可以合法做单变量 param-only 探针。建议本轮以 r138 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`，直接测试“shared low-rank basis + 单 routed expert + residual cleanup”能否把这条 hetero MoE 线从约 0.60x 压到约 0.52x total_cost，并保持足够接近 r138 的质量。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
